Description: WLANPi Front Panel Menu System 2
 Decoupled FPMS architecture for WLANPi hardware.
 .
 A FastAPI state service acts as the single source of truth.
 All system data is fetched from wlanpi-core via HMAC-authenticated REST.
 Thin clients (OLED screen, Textual TUI, Cockpit plugin) subscribe via
 WebSocket and render the same state independently.
 .
 Includes a pluggable complications API for third-party status indicators.
